# Credit_Risk_Assessment_System
# 🚀 Overview
A machine learning project to predict loan default risk using classification models. Built for fintech and banking applications.

# 🔧 Tools & Technologies
- Python (Pandas, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib)
- Logistic Regression
- Power BI (Dashboarding)
# 📊 Key Features
- Feature engineering from raw loan data
- ROC-AUC analysis for model evaluation
- Interactive dashboard for business insights
# 📁 Structure
- notebooks: EDA and modeling
- src: Python scripts
- powerbi: Dashboard files
- README.md: Project guide
# 📈 Results
Achieved ROC-AUC score of 0.85 with logistic regression. Dashboard highlights risk segments and approval trends.
